<plot>Plates is the story of the inspirational bond formed between a third grade teacher and his "quietest" student. Forced together by a mother with more professional skills than parenting abilities, Mr. McCloskey (Sam R. Ross) and Izzy (Kennedy Noel) embark together on a journey of self discovery. Izzy finds the nurturing and compassionate adult that she has always needed while Mr. McCloskey finally learns the importance and power of being a teacher.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?434918</url></doc>
